title: [Boreas Meadows, Ostria Court]
description: The road ends here where a tall tree stands amidst the grasses, its branches swaying gently in the breeze.  The trill of a bird can occasionally be heard from above.  A worn wooden bench rests beneath the tree while wild roses run rampant on bushes growing low to the ground.
